  "title": "WLAN不定时断开重连，提示\"已连接XXX网络\"怎么办？",
  "answer": " <p style=\"margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:4.0pt;margin-left:77.95pt;text-indent:-21.25pt;line-height:12.0pt;tab-stops:63.0pt list 77.95pt;layout-grid-mode:char;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Arial','sans-serif';tab-stops:list 77.95pt\">1.       连接 WLAN 成功后，请保持在 WLAN 热点的有效距离内，避免由于距离太远导致网络信号弱从而自动断开。</p> <p style=\"margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:4.0pt;margin-left:106.3pt;line-height:12.0pt;layout-grid-mode:char;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Arial','sans-serif'\"> </p> <p style=\"margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:4.0pt;margin-left:77.95pt;text-indent:-21.25pt;line-height:12.0pt;tab-stops:63.0pt list 77.95pt;layout-grid-mode:char;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Arial','sans-serif';tab-stops:list 77.95pt\">2.       进入 WLAN 设置界面，点击“高级设置 > 在休眠状态下保持 WLAN 连接”，选择“始终”。手机将始终保持与 WLAN 网络的连接。</p> <p style=\"margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:4.0pt;margin-left:106.3pt;line-height:12.0pt;layout-grid-mode:char;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Arial','sans-serif';text-align:center\" align=\"center\">![](http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=SupportImage&imagePath=/20150916205919105001.gif)</p> <p style=\"margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:4.0pt;margin-left:77.95pt;text-indent:-21.25pt;line-height:12.0pt;tab-stops:63.0pt list 77.95pt;layout-grid-mode:char;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Arial','sans-serif';tab-stops:list 77.95pt\">3.       若问题依然存在，请重新打开 WLAN 开关或重启 WLAN 热点。</p> <p style=\"margin-top:8.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:8.0pt;margin-left:51.05pt;line-height:12.0pt;layout-grid-mode:char;punctuation-trim:leading;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Arial','sans-serif';line-height:normal\">* 图示仅供参考，具体操作请以手机实际界面为准</p>",
